title: $:/plugins/tobibeer/external/config

Configure external wikis under `$:/config/ExternalWiki/<wiki name>` specifying:

; text
: the url of the wiki (w/o final `#`)
; top
: a top margin ignored when rendering, e.g. wiki header
; link
: whether to display a link to the title
; height
: default iframe height for wiki

These defaults provide global fallbacks:

